  questions:
  - questionInfo: What did Harry use to stay in the water at the Triwizard Tournament?
    questionType: 0
    questionImg: {fileID: 0}
    questionClip: {fileID: 0}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 0}
    options:
    - An air bubble
    - Turned into a shark
    - Gillyweed
    - A snorkel
    correctAns: Gillyweed
  - questionInfo: What does Snape first ask Harry in potions class in the first film?
    questionType: 0
    questionImg: {fileID: 0}
    questionClip: {fileID: 0}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 0}
    options:
    - What would I get if I added powdered root of asphodel to an infusion of wormwood?
    - where would you look if I told you to find me a bezoar?
    - What is the difference, Potter, between monkshood and wolfsbane?
    - Not so bright after all, are we, Potter?
    correctAns: What would I get if I added powdered root of asphodel to an infusion
      of wormwood?
  - questionInfo: What position did Fred and George play in Quidditch?
    questionType: 0
    questionImg: {fileID: 0}
    questionClip: {fileID: 0}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 0}
    options:
    - Beaters
    - Chaser
    - Keepers
    - One was a beater and another was a chaser
    correctAns: Beaters
